WEBVTT

00:03:58.148 --> 00:04:00.413
or "Yep. Yeah.

00:04:00.437 --> 00:04:01.907
That's just the way it is."

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:08.359
But somehow, no one ever talks about
the person who took the cell phone.

00:04:09.246 --> 00:04:11.594
Overly simplified, I get it,

00:04:11.618 --> 00:04:13.891
but you see where I'm going.

00:04:15.026 --> 00:04:18.452
Men are so used to helping
themselves, that it's like ...

00:04:19.118 --> 00:04:20.591
they can't help themselves.

00:04:22.482 --> 00:04:26.204
And not because men
are fundamentally less moral,

00:04:26.228 --> 00:04:31.944
but because this is a very big
blind spot for most men.